---
import Base from "../layouts/base.astro";
---

<Base title="Clarity. — Why Insight-as-a-Service?">
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-24 text-center">
    <!-- Heading sits visually above the box -->
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-4 leading-tight">
      Why Insight-as-a-Service?
    </h1>

    <!-- Why Insight-as-a-Service Explainer -->
    <section
      class="mt-[1rem] bg-gray-900 text-white py-16 px-6 rounded-lg text-center"
    >
      <p class="text-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8 leading-relaxed">
        Hiring a consultancy feels like spinning up a project.<br />
        Hiring a contractor feels like buying time.<br /> Neither gives you what
        you actually need: consistent, strategic support without the overhead.
      </p>

      <p class="text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-4 opacity-90">
        That's why we built Insight-as-a-Service.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8 opacity-90">
        It's a monthly support plan — not a proposal, not a headcount. You get
        access to strategic expertise, delivered with context and continuity,
        through a lightweight, tiered model that flexes with your needs.
      </p>

      <p class="text-xl font-semibold">
        No procurement stress. No rebriefs. No surprises. Just Clarity.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Why IaaS grid -->
    <section class="mt-20 text-left">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-black/20 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-center">
            Outcome Clarity.
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-center">
            Know exactly what to build and why. <br />No more guessing, scope
            creep, or wasted effort.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-black/20 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-center">
            Embedded Expertise.
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-center">
            We integrate into your team, not just your calendar.<br /> No bloated
            decks. Just actionable insight.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-black/20 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-center">
            Predictable Cost.
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-center">
            Frictionless support plans with fixed scope. <br />High impact. No
            surprises. No extras.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-black/20 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 text-center">
            Strategic Continuity.
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-center">
            No stop-start engagements or endless SoWs. <br />Consistent
            thinking, context & momentum.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Final CTA -->
    <section
      id="final-cta"
      class="mt-20 bg-gray-900 text-white py-12 px-6 rounded-lg text-center"
    >
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Still unsure?</h2>
      <p class="mb-6 text-lg">
        That's why Clarity exists.<br /> You don't need all the answers, just a better
        way to find them. <br /><br />No fluff. No spam. Just Clarity.<br /><br
        />
      </p>
      <a
        href="/"
        class="inline-block bg-white text-black font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded hover:bg-gray-200 transition"
        >Join the Waitlist</a
      >
    </section>
  </main>
</Base>
